le should also provide benefits that will accrue directly to clients in the form of increased commitments to technology back office and compliance as well as in form of an expanded research effort supported by a team of  investment professionals investment management firms depend on the quality of the people providing portfolio management research and client relationship services said david tillson president of eagle ridge investment management llc  david laidlaws and his colleagues professionalism enabled laidlaw group to thrive over the course of two wrenching bear markets laidlaw group and eagle ridge share the same fundamental approach to longterm investing said david laidlaw founder of laidlaw group llc this merger will allow each firm to enhance the investment research and service it provides without sacrificing the unique qualities that attracted clients in the first place its an exciting step for both companies and everyone involved is enthusiastic about what this partnership could mean for both clients interests and the future growth of the merged firm about eagle ridge investment management llc eagle ridge investment management is an independent ria with offices in westport ct and bedford hills ny the firm specializes in investment management strategies for clients and currently serves roughly  different households families individuals and institutions for more information visit wwweagleridgeinvestmentcom source eagle ridge investment management llc related links httpwwweagleridgeinvestmentcom view table fullscreen view table fullscreen journalists and bloggers the news you need when you need it join pr newswire for journalists to access all of the free services designated to make your job easier in need of subject matter experts for your story submit a free profnet request and find the sources you need learn more my news release contains wide tables view fullscreen looking to send a news release with pr newswire take advantage of the worlds leading distri